///git command///

->git init
->git remote add origin "http....(repository link).git"
->git add .
->git commit -m "initial commit"
->git push



///when deploy the reactjs app or project in github using git this command want to write the command prompt in folderlocation(cmd)///

->npm install gh-pages--save-dev
->npm run deploy


//updates the files in github so using this command///

->git add .
->git commit -m"update commit"
->git push




